{"id":958,"date":"2020-11-07T10:15:38","date_gmt":"2020-11-07T15:15:38","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/bhide.net\/?p=958"},"modified":"2020-11-07T10:30:34","modified_gmt":"2020-11-07T15:30:34","slug":"growing-scholarships-offered-by-the-indian-women-scientists-association","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/growing-scholarships-offered-by-the-indian-women-scientists-association\/","title":{"rendered":"Growing scholarships offered by the Indian Women Scientists Association."},"content":{"rendered":"<div data-contents=\"true\">\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"aabqi\" data-offset-key=\"2949v-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"2949v-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"2949v-0-0\">Good to see their <a href=\"https:\/\/iwsa.net\/community-programs\/iwsa-scholarship\/\">scholarships for &#8220;girl students&#8221; in science<\/a> (;-)) keeps growing.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"aabqi\" data-offset-key=\"5a15q-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"5a15q-0-0\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"aabqi\" data-offset-key=\"b790c-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"b790c-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"b790c-0-0\">I gave one in my parent&#8217;s name some years ago.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"aabqi\" data-offset-key=\"b7c25-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"b7c25-0-0\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"aabqi\" data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\">\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\">My mother was <a href=\"https:\/\/iwsa.net\/about-us\/founder-members\/\">a founding member<\/a> and later served as its President. My father&#8217;s support for her remarkable life and career was itself remarkable: He found her (an unfunded) phd slot in Brussels, paid for, and pushed her to go. I was 18 months old when she left India and she didnt come back till she finished her phd.. In between, my father was the &#8220;single parent.&#8221; (All that in the 1950s!)<\/span><\/div>\n<div data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\">https:\/\/iwsa.net\/community-programs\/iwsa-scholarship\/<\/div>\n<div data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\"><\/div>\n<div data-offset-key=\"6aqnn-0-0\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-959\" src=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/IWSA-scholarships.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"910\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/IWSA-scholarships.jpg 910w, https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/IWSA-scholarships-300x258.jpg 300w, https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/IWSA-scholarships-768x660.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 910px) 100vw, 910px\" \/><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Good to see their scholarships for &#8220;girl students&#8221; in science (;-)) keeps growing. I gave one in my parent&#8217;s name<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":true,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"colormag_page_container_layout":"default_layout","colormag_page_sidebar_layout":"default_layout","footnotes":"","_links_to":"","_links_to_target":""},"categories":[35],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-958","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-ruminations"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/958","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json